#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.112"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.112:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.112:0.2"
msgid "11. Sambodhavagga"
msgstr "11. Awakening"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.112:0.3"
msgid "112. Dutiyanidānasutta"
msgstr "112. Sources (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.264"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.112:1.1"
msgid "“Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, nidānāni kammānaṃ samudayāya."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three sources that give rise to deeds."

msgctxt "an3.112:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.112:1.3"
msgid "Atīte, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando jāyati;"
msgstr ""
"Desire comes up for things that stimulate desire and greed in the past, "
"future, or present."

msgctxt "an3.112:1.4"
msgid "anāgate, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando jāyati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:1.5"
msgid ""
"paccuppanne, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando jāyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:1.6"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, atīte chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando jāyati?"
msgstr ""
"And how does desire come up for things that stimulate desire and greed in "
"the past, future, or present?"

msgctxt "an3.112:1.7"
msgid ""
"Atīte, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha cetasā anuvitakketi "
"anuvicāreti."
msgstr ""
"In your heart you think about and consider things that stimulate desire and "
"greed in the past, future, or present."

msgctxt "an3.112:1.8"
msgid ""
"Tassa atīte chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha cetasā anuvitakkayato "
"anuvicārayato chando jāyati."
msgstr "When you do this, desire comes up,"

msgctxt "an3.112:1.9"
msgid "Chandajāto tehi dhammehi saṃyutto hoti."
msgstr "and you get attached to those things."

msgctxt "an3.112:1.10"
msgid "Etamahaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃyojanaṃ vadāmi yo cetaso sārāgo."
msgstr "This lust in the heart is what I call a fetter."

msgctxt "an3.112:1.11"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, atīte chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando jāyati."
msgstr ""
"That’s how desire comes up for things that stimulate desire and lust in the "
"past, future, or present."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.112:2.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, anāgate chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando jāyati?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:2.2"
msgid ""
"Anāgate, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha cetasā anuvitakketi "
"anuvicāreti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:2.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa anāgate chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha cetasā anuvitakkayato "
"anuvicārayato chando jāyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:2.4"
msgid "Chandajāto tehi dhammehi saṃyutto hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:2.5"
msgid "Etamahaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃyojanaṃ vadāmi yo cetaso sārāgo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:2.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, anāgate chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando jāyati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.112:3.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, paccuppanne chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando "
"jāyati?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:3.2"
msgid ""
"Paccuppanne, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha cetasā "
"anuvitakketi anuvicāreti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:3.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa paccuppanne chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha cetasā anuvitakkayato "
"anuvicārayato chando jāyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:3.4"
msgid "Chandajāto tehi dhammehi saṃyutto hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:3.5"
msgid "Etamahaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃyojanaṃ vadāmi yo cetaso sārāgo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:3.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, paccuppanne chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando "
"jāyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:3.7"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi nidānāni kammānaṃ samudayāya."
msgstr "These are three sources that give rise to deeds."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.265"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.112:4.1"
msgid "Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, nidānāni kammānaṃ samudayāya."
msgstr "There are these three sources that give rise to deeds."

msgctxt "an3.112:4.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.112:4.3"
msgid "Atīte, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando na jāyati;"
msgstr ""
"Desire doesn’t come up for things that stimulate desire and lust in the "
"past, future, or present."

msgctxt "an3.112:4.4"
msgid "anāgate, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando na jāyati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:4.5"
msgid ""
"paccuppanne, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando na jāyati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.112:5.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, atīte chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando na "
"jāyati?"
msgstr ""
"And how does desire not come up for things that stimulate desire and lust in "
"the past, future, or present?"

msgctxt "an3.112:5.2"
msgid ""
"Atītānaṃ, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniyānaṃ dhammānaṃ āyatiṃ vipākaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"You understand the future result of things that stimulate desire and lust in "
"the past, future, or present."

msgctxt "an3.112:5.3"
msgid "Āyatiṃ vipākaṃ viditvā tadabhinivatteti."
msgstr "When you know this, you grow disillusioned,"

#. VAR: Tadabhinivattetvā → tadabhinivajjetvā (bj, s1-3, km) | tad abhinivaddhetvā (pts1)
#. VAR: abhinivijjhitvā → abhivirājetvā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
#. VAR: ativijjha → abhinivijjha (mr)
msgctxt "an3.112:5.4"
msgid "Tadabhinivattetvā cetasā abhinivijjhitvā paññāya ativijjha passati."
msgstr ""
"your heart becomes dispassionate, and you see it with penetrating wisdom."

msgctxt "an3.112:5.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, atīte chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando na "
"jāyati."
msgstr ""
"That’s how desire doesn’t come up for things that stimulate desire and lust "
"in the past, future, or present."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an3.112:6.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, anāgate chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando na "
"jāyati?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:6.2"
msgid ""
"Anāgatānaṃ, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniyānaṃ dhammānaṃ āyatiṃ vipākaṃ "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:6.3"
msgid "Āyatiṃ vipākaṃ viditvā tadabhinivatteti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:6.4"
msgid "Tadabhinivattetvā cetasā abhinivijjhitvā paññāya ativijjha passati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:6.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, anāgate chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando na "
"jāyati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an3.112:7.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, paccuppanne chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando na "
"jāyati?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:7.2"
msgid ""
"Paccuppannānaṃ, bhikkhave, chandarāgaṭṭhāniyānaṃ dhammānaṃ āyatiṃ vipākaṃ "
"pajānāti, āyatiṃ vipākaṃ viditvā tadabhinivatteti, tadabhinivattetvā cetasā "
"abhinivijjhitvā paññāya ativijjha passati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:7.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, paccuppanne chandarāgaṭṭhāniye dhamme ārabbha chando na "
"jāyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.112:7.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi nidānāni kammānaṃ samudayāyā”ti."
msgstr "These are three sources that give rise to deeds.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.112:7.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.112:7.6"
msgid "Sambodhavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an3.112:8.1"
msgid "Pubbeva duve assādā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.112:8.2"
msgid "Samaṇo ruṇṇapañcamaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.112:8.3"
msgid "Atitti dve ca vuttāni,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.112:8.4"
msgid "Nidānāni apare duveti."
msgstr ""
